data.description: Must See to believe! Amazing Kailua, Oahu home with 360 degree Ocean and Mountain views. This comfortable and private ridge top location is a great place to relax and enjoy the country living from above Kailua Town with the convenience of Honolulu less than 30 minute away. You will see World Class beaches Kailua, Lanikai and Waimanalo plus the Koolau Mountains from your own yard. Home has 3 spacious bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, two with washers and dryers. Electric Vehicle charging.   Buyers do their due diligence. Tenants on month-to-month great rental income. Tax records have not been updated to reflect new permitted square footage and value. When making offer please include As-Is Addendum, POF & (Conditional Loan Approval Letter) with offer. There are no CPR association fees due. Easement with neighboring house for driveway and utilities only. All offers will be considered.
